---
title: Raspberry Pi Home Server
description: Building a capable home server on a Raspberry Pi — media center, VPN gateway, and secure remote access.
status: active
order: 1
---

A series on turning a Raspberry Pi into a full home server. Covers hardware setup, running your own media center with Plex, setting up VPN split-tunneling to route your TV through another country, and exposing everything securely without opening ports.
